    <item>
      <title>Moncler 投资者 Rivetti 家族将离开最高股东集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/moncler-investor-rivetti-family-to-leave-top-shareholder-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Moncler SpA 的顶级股东周六表示，以 Stone Island 运动服装品牌闻名的家族将以“合作”方式退出这家豪华蓬松夹克制造商的投资工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/moncler-investor-rivetti-family-to-leave-top-shareholder-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 16:34:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者纷纷逃离曾经被誉为“下一个特斯拉”的电动汽车新贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/investors-flee-tumbling-ev-upstarts-once-hailed-as-next-tesla</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾经有一段时间，世界上一些财力最雄厚的公司的支持以及仅仅销售电动汽车的雄心就足以激发人们对新贵 Rivian Automotive Inc. 和 Lucid Group Inc. 股票的信心。现在投资者几乎已经认输了在股票上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/investors-flee-tumbling-ev-upstarts-once-hailed-as-next-tesla</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚总统称中国和印度签署债务重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/zambian-president-says-china-and-india-signed-debt-revamp-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈坎德·希奇莱马周六表示，中国和印度是赞比亚债务重组最后需要签署协议的两个国家，它们终于签署了协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/zambian-president-says-china-and-india-signed-debt-revamp-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 14:46:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房地产公司 Avison Young 即将在违约后进行重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/real-estate-firm-avison-young-defaults-on-canada-loan-s-p-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[房地产服务公司 Avison Young (Canada) Inc. 表示，在拖欠高级定期贷款并导致评级下调后，该公司即将完成重组以清理其资产负债表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/real-estate-firm-avison-young-defaults-on-canada-loan-s-p-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 14:22:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
